      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, always keeping it tucked away in a garage. There isn't a single scratch or ding to be found; it\u2019s just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, I promise you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
