      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and double VANOS for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with mechanical precision, sending power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. This chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. Suspension bushings and dampers are in peak operational condition, preserving the telepathic steering response and signature 50/50 weight balance. The interior is immaculate, with no bolster wear or dead pixels, reflecting its meticulously documented service history. A true turn-key masterpiece for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
